title: Episode 323: Drop the Pin (Feat. Capella Grey & Dr. Victoria Zdrok)
itunes:title: Episode 323: Drop the Pin (Feat. Capella Grey & Dr. Victoria Zdrok)
description:
Singer Capella Grey and Playmate/Sex Therapist, Dr. Victoria Zdrok join the ladies of Lip Service this week. During this week's conversation, Dr. Zdrok analyzes Capella's answers to hypothetical situations, she gives insight as to life as a playmate during the '90s, as well as giving tips on how to last longer in bed. Capella Grey opens up about his experience with a sugar momma, his struggles with taking 'breaks' in relationships, his love for threesomes, and much more. Enjoy!
